1
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:43,760
Did Ling Yizhou send Ms. Huang
to spy on me?

2
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,840
Where are the marriage certificates?

3
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,280
MARRIAGE CERTIFICATE

4
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,120
Do you recall anything, Mumu?

5
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,680
A bit. This seems familiar.

6
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,200
Did something happen here?

7
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,720
Look.

8
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,880
How cute!
How come he's dressed so formally?

9
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,920
Is he attending a ceremony?

10
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:30,800
Yes.

11
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,520
What is it?

12
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,360
Was I there?

13
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:38,520
The ceremony was held just for you.

14
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:52,720
Aren't these photos of me from my drama?

15
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,480
How come you're in them too?

16
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,240
This is such terrible photoshopping!

17
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,040
Don't tell me you made this.

18
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,000
Mumu.

19
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,240
You had the same reaction that day.

20
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,640
It was right here.

21
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:31,560
This is where I proposed to you.

22
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,560
Proposed?

23
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:39,360
That day,

24
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,160
I told you I was sorry

25
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,320
that I couldn't take part in your past,

26
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:46,040
so I edited these photos
to make it up to you.

27
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:50,000
I told you

28
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,160
that I would watch
the sunset and stars with you.

29
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,680
I would grow old with you.

30
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,680
All I hoped for

31
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,280
was to be able to be in your world.

32
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,720
You agreed.

33
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,480
You said yes.

34
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,560
Sorry, I...

35
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:42,120
I really don't remember.

36
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,480
It's okay.

37
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,960
Let's go to the next place.

38
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,360
You were sitting right here.

39
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:02,800
Jia Fei was in this seat.

40
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,600
I was behind you.

41
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,040
Wen Li was over there.

42
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:10,200
Is this the last place?

43
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:13,080
This is a very important location for us.

44
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,280
Do you remember anything?

45
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:21,000
Do you remember why we came here?

46
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,280
I was at the office one day

47
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:25,920
when Wen Li showed me

48
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,520
a photo of you and Jia Fei
at the gym with personal trainers.

49
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,840
We got jealous.

50
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,320
We immediately drove there.

51
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:35,320
Why would you be jealous of a gym trainer?

52
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,880
I just was.

53
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:41,360
You told me you liked watching
muscular studs bursting with testosterone.

54
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,680
So we came here.

55
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,880
I had Wen Li arrange a ball game for you.

56
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,920
We were sitting right here.

57
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,840
We were watching the game.

58
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,840
Everything was going well.

59
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,200
Everybody was cheering and clapping.

60
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,480
But I didn't know

61
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,640
that you and Jia Fei
had never been to a game before.

62
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:02,240
You didn't know which team
we were supposed to be rooting for.

63
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:05,000
We wore red jerseys
so we should be cheering for the red team.

64
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,560
But when the blue team scored a goal,

65
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:09,520
you and Jia Fei jumped up,
started hugging, and yelled out,

66
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,560
"Yes! Goal! Way to go!"

67
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,040
There was a guy over here.

68
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,040
I don't know how he managed to do it.

69
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,640
He ripped off the seat

70
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,880
and threw it at us.

71
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,160
You were below us
and I was afraid you would get hurt.

72
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:24,800
So I hauled him up here
and we started fighting.

73
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,400
He punched me,

74
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,520
so I fought back.

75
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,440
Mumu, are you okay?

76
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,240
He kicked me right in the stomach.

77
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,520
You were right here.

78
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:10,160
I said, "Stop it! Don't hurt Mumu!"

79
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,040
I pushed him away

80
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,920
and dragged him up there,
but he was so strong.

81
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,160
-Stop fighting.
-He punched me again.

82
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:18,760
-Then I punched him back.
-Enough, stop it!

83
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,880
It's okay. I can keep acting.

84
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,440
It's enough.

85
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,800
Did you remember something?

86
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,919
I remembered some.

87
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:36,120
Do you remember where we went afterward?

88
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,919
-Afterward?
-Yes.

89
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,360
We went to the Civil Affairs Bureau.

90
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,640
-Civil Affairs Bureau?
-Remember?

91
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,040
You dragged me there.

92
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,920
Was I that forward?

93
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,720
On the way there,

94
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,400
you said that

95
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,640
<i>our marriage was a scheme.</i>

96
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,440
<i>My scheme.</i>

97
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,960
<i>But you didn't mind
helping my scheme succeed.</i>

98
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,920
It's okay if you don't remember.

99
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,800
Let's go to the Civil Affairs Bureau.

100
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:14,160
I'll act it out for you.
Maybe you'll remember something.

101
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,680
You don't have to.

102
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,760
I believe you.

103
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,160
What did you say?

104
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,560
You once said that

105
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:38,240
even if you forget everything,
you wouldn't forget me.

106
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,200
I'm not giving up on you
because you've lost your memory.

107
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:48,920
Even if your past is blank for you,

108
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,560
there will be a future.

109
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:57,040
I will be here for you from now on, okay?

110
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,240
Before I agreed to your terms,

111
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,320
I thought

112
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:13,280
about leaving you no matter what.

113
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,400
But everybody said we were in love.

114
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,960
Without my memories,

115
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,760
this love doesn't feel real to me.

116
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:27,040
After moving in with you,

117
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,560
I fell into your trap.

118
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,880
It became harder
to distance myself from you.

119
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,640
Just now,

120
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,960
when you stood in front of me

121
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:47,640
the fuzzy memories in my mind
turned crystal clear.

122
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:52,800
And this.

123
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,880
This is the ring you gave me.

124
00:10:57,240 --> 00:11:00,920
My subconscious mind
still remembers this ring.

125
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,760
Ling Yizhou.

126
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:10,880
Thank you for not giving up on me.

127
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,160
For not giving up

128
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,000
on the love we had.

129
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:19,240
If this was your scheme,

130
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,160
then I won't mind

131
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,200
helping you succeed once again.

132
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,160
<i>It's recording.</i>

133
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:20,240
<i>This is Xia Lin and Ling Yizhou's
wedding planning vlog series,</i>

134
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:22,680
<i>wedding photos edition!</i>

135
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,920
Mumu, do we have to film everything?

136
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,320
Of course.

137
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,880
This only happens once.

138
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,880
I want everything on film

139
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,960
so I can watch it when we're old.

140
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:36,120
All right, you're up now.

141
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,160
Okay.

142
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:39,560
<i>On the second of next month,</i>

143
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:43,360
<i>the wedding dresses we ordered
should be ready.</i>

144
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,480
I'll take Mumu to the fitting
on the third.

145
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:48,680
The sixth and seventh
will be for a two-day photo shoot.

146
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:50,480
We'll get to pick out the photos
on the eighth.

147
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,680
-On the ninth, we'll--
-Stop.

148
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:56,240
Ling Yizhou, I just realized
how old-school you are.

149
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:58,640
Did you come up with this schedule?

150
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,280
Of course. This is our wedding.

151
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:02,160
I want to plan everything myself.

152
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:04,760
How do you have time for this
with your busy schedule?

153
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,960
Weren't you the one who said it?

154
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:10,480
Wedding photos are very important to you.

155
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:14,040
I'm more than happy to take the time
to plan this out for you.

156
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,600
<i>Wedding photos are important,</i>

157
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:18,520
but I don't want them taken
just for the sake of taking them.

158
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:21,400
I want our wedding photos to be meaningful

159
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:23,480
and capture a genuine snapshot of us.

160
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,560
-Right.
-When we look at our photos later,

161
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:29,840
we'll be able to reminisce
about these beautiful moments.

162
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,200
Most importantly,

163
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:34,440
I must wear an Alex Wang wedding gown.

164
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:38,080
I think my plan is perfect already,

165
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:41,440
but if you have any opinions,

166
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:42,840
I'll respect them.

167
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:47,520
I don't have a lot of energy

168
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:49,840
to spend on this though.

169
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:51,560
Why?

170
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,080
Are you feeling sick?

171
00:13:57,880 --> 00:13:59,080
Take a guess.

172
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,200
You're kidding.

173
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,480
Is it what I'm thinking?

174
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:14,200
Are you serious? I'm going to be a father?

175
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:15,680
<i>Wait, you have to tell me.</i>

176
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,880
<i>I need you to say the words.</i>

177
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,240
You can't...

178
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,480
Is it true?

179
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,520
Yes.

180
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,760
I'm a father.

181
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,240
Sorry, I'm just...

182
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:26,960
I don't know what...

183
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,160
Mumu, this is...

184
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:33,240
Ling Yizhou, thank you for waiting.

185
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:37,080
You've given me time and respect
during the time I forgot about you.

186
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:39,800
I had actually fallen in love with you
all over again

187
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:41,800
before my memory returned.

188
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,400
I told you we were meant to be!

189
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:47,360
But we have to push up our wedding

190
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:50,480
or I won't be able to fit
into Alex Wang wedding dress.

191
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:51,640
What about this?

192
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,480
We can wait for the baby to be born first.

193
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:54,840
-Then we can have--
-No!

194
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:56,080
We're not postponing the wedding!

195
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:57,720
Sit down.

196
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,800
The wedding will be held as planned.

197
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:02,880
We'll have our wedding photos
on the sixth and seventh.

198
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,120
<i>Then we'll pick out the photos.</i>

199
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:05,280
<i>Boss.</i>

200
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:08,800
Bojue Photography has built up
a good reputation.

201
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:11,000
Orders keep increasing.

202
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:12,320
If this keeps up,

203
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,600
we might not be able
to deal with the demand.

204
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:18,840
Even so, we have to maintain
the quality of our products

205
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:20,360
and attentive service.

206
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:23,400
We're not just aiming to be
the biggest brand.

207
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:25,480
-We also aim to be the best.
-Yes.

208
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,080
By the way,

209
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:30,040
there is a particular case
that requires your attention.

210
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:33,560
This customer claims to be
your hardcore fan

211
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,760
and has been following you
since your debut.

212
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:40,560
She was sorry
that you retired from showbiz.

213
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:43,400
She said that she hopes
to receive her idol's well wishes

214
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:45,320
in the happiest moment of her life.

215
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:50,680
Okay.

216
00:15:51,160 --> 00:15:52,680
I'll supervise the photo shoot myself.

217
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,480
Smile a little wider.

218
00:15:59,040 --> 00:16:00,080
Very good.

219
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,560
Move in a little closer.

220
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:07,200
Yes, smile.

221
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,240
Big smile!

222
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:09,880
Good work, everyone.

223
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:11,840
-Hi, Mr. Chu.
-Hi, Mr. Chu.

224
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,160
-Here.
-Is this really happening?

225
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,920
Hello, I'm Chu Yan.

226
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:19,520
Hi!

227
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,560
I think this shot is...

228
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:22,760
Sorry, I'm so excited.

229
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:25,520
Huohuo, even though
you're no longer acting,

230
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:28,920
I'm really happy to hear that
you're succeeding in another field.

231
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:30,400
You'll always be my idol.

232
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,560
Keep persevering.

233
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:35,680
My husband and I will always support
you and your career.

234
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:37,760
Thank you.

235
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,120
Thank you for supporting me

236
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:41,280
and supporting Bojue Photography.

237
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:42,520
Thank you.

238
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,920
BOJUE PHOTOGRAPHY

239
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,360
We should get back to the photo shoot.

240
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:46,720
When we're done,

241
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,560
I'll make sure to spread the word
on social media.

242
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:51,040
Thank you. I'll let you get back to it.

243
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:52,440
-Okay.
-Let's go.

244
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:56,360
-Here we go.
-Ready.

245
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:57,920
-Let's continue.
-All ready.

246
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:58,840
Okay.

247
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:03,320
There you go!
That's the smile we're looking for.

248
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,119
Good!

249
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:08,000
-<i>Hello, Chu Yan?</i>
-Now for a different angle.

250
00:17:08,079 --> 00:17:11,200
<i>Do you want to stay in or go out tomorrow?</i>

251
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:12,359
A little closer. Good.

252
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:16,000
-Don't worry. I'll pick you up tomorrow.
-Good. Beautiful.

253
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:21,920
<i>Is something big happening today?</i>

254
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:23,839
<i>Boss is all smiles!</i>

255
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,680
<i>Does this mean
we don't need to work overtime?</i>

256
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,200
<i>What does it mean?</i>

257
00:17:28,319 --> 00:17:29,640
<i>Please wait patiently.</i>

258
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:31,480
<i>Don't hold back on us!</i>

259
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:34,320
<i>Drop some hints! Curiosity killed the cat!</i>

260
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:38,040
<i>I have a feeling
it's a once-in-a-lifetime happy occasion!</i>

261
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,600
<i>Could it be...</i>

262
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:42,000
Wen Li, go buy some books

263
00:17:42,280 --> 00:17:45,680
about pregnancy
and diet and nutrition for pregnant women.

264
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:46,800
-Okay.
-One more thing.

265
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:50,040
Aren't there any classes
for expectant fathers?

266
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:51,720
-Sign me up for them.
-Okay.

