Pidan!

530
00:34:45,679 --> 00:34:46,679
Look!

531
00:34:48,040 --> 00:34:50,360
-So cute!
-Adorable!

532
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:16,080
Feifei, catch!

533
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:17,600
-We're ready! Over here!
-Over here.

534
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:20,840
-Over here!
-One, two, three!

535
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,520
Feifei, when will you marry Wen Li?

536
00:36:27,040 --> 00:36:28,960
-Good question!
-How could that happen?

537
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:30,560
He stole the bouquet!

538
00:37:00,240 --> 00:37:02,640
Are you drunk?

539
00:37:03,160 --> 00:37:04,320
Should we leave?

540
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:06,280
No, I haven't been drinking.

541
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,760
I wanted to ask you something.

542
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:12,160
You said before
that you have a fear of men.

543
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:14,280
Were you lying to me?

544
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:16,280
No, it's true!

545
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,480
I swear!

546
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:20,560
A man came into contact with you.

547
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,720
You didn't seem to have a reaction.

548
00:37:28,120 --> 00:37:29,000
What is it?

549
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:30,680
Did you really lie to me?

550
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,920
No.

551
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:35,200
Chu Yan, do you know?

552
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,960
Ever since I met you,

553
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:39,120
my fear of men has slowly lessened.

554
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:42,240
I seem to be able
to interact normally with men now.

555
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:45,840
The doctor said I won't need
regular psychological therapy anymore.

556
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:49,000
That's great.

557
00:37:50,240 --> 00:37:52,040
Are you unhappy?

558
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:54,560
No, why would I be?

559
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,880
You can interact with others
like a normal person.

560
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:58,680
I'm happy for you.

561
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:00,200
Really.

562
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,040
But...

563
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:05,200
You'll always be the most special one.

564
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:10,680
Of course.

565
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:43,800
This looks great!

566
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:48,720
It's nice!

567
00:38:48,840 --> 00:38:50,440
What do you think? Pretty good, right?

568
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:52,280
I had it specially made for you.

569
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:53,440
Thank you, Chu Yan.

570
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:54,480
I love it.

571
00:38:54,560 --> 00:38:56,040
Now I want another photo shoot next year.

572
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:57,440
We'll take our son for it next year.

573
00:38:57,640 --> 00:38:58,720
Okay.

574
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,800
Me too!

575
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,000
I want to take photos too.

576
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:21,560
Let's go for a photo shoot in a few days.

577
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:23,000
Don't butt in.

578
00:39:23,200 --> 00:39:24,840
I want to take photos with Linlin.

579
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:28,160
We'll bring Ruan Meng too
and we'll have a photoshoot among friends.

580
00:39:28,240 --> 00:39:29,720
-Okay!
-No problem.

581
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:32,440
You can have a photo shoot
with whomever you want

582
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:35,080
and wherever you want.

583
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:37,840
Yes!

584
00:39:38,560 --> 00:39:39,400
Great!

585
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:43,320
In that case,
I'm going to plan a no-men vacation.

586
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:45,840
What do you say, ladies?

587
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,720
-Yes!
-Yes!

588
00:39:48,040 --> 00:39:50,360
Chu Yan, your business is booming.

589
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,080
Are you going to launch it into space?

590
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:54,240
If you can take me there,

591
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:56,360
I'll take photos from space.

592
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,440
FIVE YEARS LATER

593
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:23,320
The next award category

594
00:40:23,600 --> 00:40:25,120
is Best Director.

595
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,640
Please look at the screen.

596
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:30,360
TELEVISION AWARDS PRESENTATION

597
00:40:32,200 --> 00:40:34,720
BEST DIRECTOR, WU QIANG

598
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:15,160
-Our next award category...
-Congratulations.

599
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:16,560
is Best Actress.

600
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:18,000
Please look at the screen.

601
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:24,680
TELEVISION AWARDS PRESENTATION

602
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:26,560
BEST ACTRESS, XIA LIN

603
00:41:27,640 --> 00:41:28,520
<i>Xia Lin.</i>

604
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:32,280
Butterfly<i> is her first suspense thriller
as the main actress.</i>

605
00:41:32,480 --> 00:41:35,000
<i>Her gripping performance as a woman
feeling insecure about the future,</i>

606
00:41:35,080 --> 00:41:36,760
-Thank you.
<i>-disappointment toward her husband,</i>

607
00:41:36,840 --> 00:41:39,880
<i>and helplessness
over her son's disobedience</i>

608
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:43,920
<i>displayed her control
over a range of complicated emotions.</i>

609
00:41:45,520 --> 00:41:46,520
Thank you.

610
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,920
-Congratulations.
-Thank you.

611
00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:58,240
Thank you.

612
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:09,360
I am extremely honored
to receive this award.

613
00:42:09,720 --> 00:42:11,360
There are many people I want to thank,

614
00:42:11,520 --> 00:42:13,040
but the one I want to thank the most

615
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:15,440
is the most special person in my life.

616
00:42:16,040 --> 00:42:19,800
In my most helpless,
uncertain, and darkest times,

617
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:21,840
he pulled me out

618
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:25,080
and gave me a spacious and liberating sky.

619
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:27,400
I became the star

620
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:30,560
that shines the brightest for him.

621
00:42:31,200 --> 00:42:32,320
Thank you.

622
00:42:46,480 --> 00:42:48,960
Next up is Best Cinematography.

623
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:50,360
Please look at the screen.

624
00:42:55,560 --> 00:42:59,560
BEST CINEMATOGRAPHY, LIN JUNBIN, LIU SHIDA

625
00:43:20,440 --> 00:43:21,560
Ling Yizhou.

626
00:43:23,880 --> 00:43:24,720
Mumu.

627
00:43:25,640 --> 00:43:27,040
You're amazing.

628
00:43:30,120 --> 00:43:31,560
I heard everything you said.

629
00:43:31,720 --> 00:43:33,200
You were wrong about one thing.

630
00:43:35,280 --> 00:43:37,200
I was the one who was saved.

631
00:43:38,400 --> 00:43:40,920
We saved each other.

632
00:43:55,280 --> 00:43:56,920
Dad! Mom!

633
00:43:58,160 --> 00:43:59,320
-Nainai!
-Nainai!

634
00:44:28,920 --> 00:44:30,880
Ling Yizhou,
I'm sleeping with Nainai tonight.

635
00:44:30,960 --> 00:44:34,240
No, don't give all your attention
to our child and ignore me.

636
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:36,560
He takes up all my energy.

637
00:44:36,840 --> 00:44:37,920
I'll give you attention later.

638
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:40,320
No. Nainai is a big boy now.

639
00:44:40,400 --> 00:44:42,360
He can sleep on his own. Don't worry.

640
00:44:42,440 --> 00:44:43,800
He's a man now.

641
00:44:45,040 --> 00:44:46,000
Dad?

642
00:44:46,800 --> 00:44:47,840
Dad?

643
00:44:49,800 --> 00:44:53,440
Can I sleep with you and Mom tonight?

644
00:44:53,520 --> 00:44:54,840
-Sure.
-No.

645
00:44:54,960 --> 00:44:57,280
Nainai, you're a man now.

646
00:44:57,360 --> 00:44:58,840
Men sleep alone.

647
00:44:59,080 --> 00:45:00,200
But...

648
00:45:00,440 --> 00:45:03,120
But you sleep with Mom.

649
00:45:03,200 --> 00:45:04,920
Aren't you a man?

650
00:45:05,160 --> 00:45:06,080
I...

651
00:45:06,880 --> 00:45:09,720
I'm a man with a wife.

652
00:45:10,040 --> 00:45:11,160
What are you saying?

653
00:45:11,320 --> 00:45:15,400
Mom, if you're my wife,
then will you sleep with me?

654
00:45:16,720 --> 00:45:19,560
Nainai, you'll have to get your own wife.

655
00:45:19,880 --> 00:45:21,120
Dad, you're so stingy.

656
00:45:21,320 --> 00:45:22,560
Who did you call stingy?

657
00:45:23,040 --> 00:45:24,600
-Who did you call stingy, Nainai?
-You, Dad!

658
00:45:24,760 --> 00:45:27,040
-Don't you run! Who did you call stingy?
-You are!

659
00:45:28,120 --> 00:45:29,640
You are, Dad!

660
00:46:35,600 --> 00:46:36,760
What's wrong, Mumu?

661
00:46:45,760 --> 00:46:46,800
Ling Yizhou?

662
00:46:48,440 --> 00:46:52,360
The two of us meeting
and falling in love was predestined.

663
00:46:54,520 --> 00:46:58,040
We'll cross paths
no matter which world we're in.

664
00:47:00,080 --> 00:47:01,200
I know.

665
00:47:29,680 --> 00:47:30,560
Where's our son?

666
00:47:30,640 --> 00:47:31,480
I don't know.

667
00:47:33,280 --> 00:47:35,600
Ling Yizhou, you must have
kicked him off the bed in your sleep!

668
00:47:35,680 --> 00:47:37,320
-It couldn't have been me!
-Search for him!

669
00:47:37,400 --> 00:47:38,520
-Nainai!
-Nainai!

670
00:47:38,760 --> 00:47:40,000
-Where are you, Nainai?
-Come out!

671
00:47:40,080 --> 00:47:41,680
-Nainai!
-Ling Yizhou, this is all your fault!

672
00:47:41,760 --> 00:47:43,360
I'll search downstairs.
You look over there.

673
00:47:43,440 --> 00:47:45,160
-You won't hear the end of this.
-Nainai!

674
00:47:45,480 --> 00:47:48,520
-Nainai!
-Where are you, Nainai?

675
00:47:49,320 --> 00:47:51,080
-Did you find him?
-No.

676
00:47:51,280 --> 00:47:52,120
He's not here either.

677
00:47:52,200 --> 00:47:53,520
-Nainai!
-Nainai!

678
00:47:53,800 --> 00:47:55,320
-Nainai, where are you?
-Come out!

679
00:47:56,000 --> 00:47:57,640
-Nainai!
-Nainai!

680
00:48:00,120 --> 00:48:03,520
<i>Mr. Ling, what rank do you think
you occupy in Xia Lin's heart?</i>

681
00:48:07,120 --> 00:48:08,040
First.

682
00:48:08,600 --> 00:48:10,040
<i>-Is that true?</i>
-Yes.

683
00:48:10,800 --> 00:48:11,720
Third.

684
00:48:13,840 --> 00:48:15,640
Nainai is first. Who's second?

685
00:48:15,720 --> 00:48:16,760
Pidan.

686
00:48:17,480 --> 00:48:19,840
<i>The next question is also for Mr. Ling.</i>

687
00:48:20,080 --> 00:48:23,000
<i>What do you think
about Xia Lin's kissing scenes?</i>

688
00:48:23,400 --> 00:48:24,480
In regards to this question,

689
00:48:24,560 --> 00:48:28,040
I feel like I've always had
an open mind about it.

690
00:48:28,480 --> 00:48:32,280
I respect all her decisions
and that's how it's always been.

691
00:48:32,960 --> 00:48:35,720
Then why wouldn't you let me accept
that drama that had kissing scenes?

692
00:48:36,120 --> 00:48:38,160
What's the next question? Moving on.

693
00:48:38,240 --> 00:48:39,320
<i>This is the last question.</i>

694
00:48:39,400 --> 00:48:42,000
<i>Do you have a message
for the fans who support you?</i>

695
00:48:42,280 --> 00:48:43,160
Sure.

696
00:48:44,680 --> 00:48:47,440
Thank you for following Mumu

697
00:48:47,600 --> 00:48:51,040
and thank you for liking the both of us.

698
00:48:52,200 --> 00:48:55,240
And I believe every person

699
00:48:55,320 --> 00:48:59,120
will be able to find their perfect love.

700
